@node "GBSYSTE" "System demands"
Systeem demands
===============
Yahtzee should run on any amiga. It's possible that on certain
machines the program will run faster/slower. If this is the case
than contact the author. This program was written on an Amiga 1200,
10MB memory, 250MB Harddisk and an 68ec20.

Minimal system demands:
Any Amiga with around 800k of free memory.

P.s.
If you have a minimal machine than you could erase Yahtzee.SFX and
Yahtzee.MOD. You don't really need these files and it will save memory!

