@node "GBHISTO" "Yahtzee history"
Yahtzee is originally a Commodore 64 game. A long... long time ago I had
Yahtzee for the C64. It looked pretty boring but it worked very well.
I then create a colour version of the game. About a year ago I even added
a Hi-score to that version. At the time, '88 or so, there wasn't a real
good Yahtzee game for the Amiga. I decided to convert the C64 version to
the Amiga and what you now see is the final result. De screen-layout is
almost exactly as the C64 version. I have to say that I tried different
screen-layouts before, including a 640x256 version, but that just didn't
work out.

